        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer827236717" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7203172465092695975">I will not attempt to add my two cents to the five decades of commentary that currently exist. But I will say this, when Malcolm says of Elijah Muhammad, &quot;My black brothers and sisters, you have come from your homes to hear-now you are <i>going</i> to hear-America&apos;s <i>wisest</i> black man! America&apos;s <i>boldest</i> black man! America&apos;s most <i>fearless</i> black man.&quot; I uttered an audible no. It was you, Malcolm. It was you.</span>
  <span id="freeText7203172465092695975" style="display:none">I will not attempt to add my two cents to the five decades of commentary that currently exist. But I will say this, when Malcolm says of Elijah Muhammad, "My black brothers and sisters, you have come from your homes to hear-now you are <i>going</i> to hear-America's <i>wisest</i> black man! America's <i>boldest</i> black man! America's most <i>fearless</i> black man." I uttered an audible no. It was you, Malcolm. It was you.</span>
