<span id="freeTextContainer15532509198899733359">I loved this book the first time I read it in 2008. I loved it this time. It is profound and moving and somehow feels timeless. Malcolm X was prophetic and powerful. His willingness to be public and be open to change is unmatched.</span>

          </span>
