<div id="review_1809974448" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1809974448" />
    <a title="Shahzad Suleman" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/61042201-shahzad-suleman"><img alt="Shahzad Suleman" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1528637085p2/61042201.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1809974448?book_show_action=true">Jan 27, 2018</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Shahzad Suleman" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Shahzad Suleman" href="/user/show/61042201-shahzad-suleman">Shahzad Suleman</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/61042201-shahzad-suleman?shelf=biographies">biographies</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1809974448" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1529683503405510784">Malcolm x, a black American Muslim, killed at the age of around 38, before completion of the book. He showed, in fact, once he was motivated no one could change more completely than the he himself who had been at the bottom of the bottom. He called himself the best example of that. He also showed that so much could be achieved in so little time. So we don’t have the excuse that life is short, in fact, we are short of purpose. Black as well as white Americans have been embracing Islam reading thi</span>
  <span id="freeText1529683503405510784" style="display:none">Malcolm x, a black American Muslim, killed at the age of around 38, before completion of the book. He showed, in fact, once he was motivated no one could change more completely than the he himself who had been at the bottom of the bottom. He called himself the best example of that. He also showed that so much could be achieved in so little time. So we don’t have the excuse that life is short, in fact, we are short of purpose. Black as well as white Americans have been embracing Islam reading this book, after his passing away. May God bless him.<br /><br />Consider this that he wasn’t a writer. Among thousands of books published every year in America, this book features in the top books by an American in last hundred years.<br /><br />I feel that if you haven’t read this book, you have done injustice to yourself.<br /><br />Ladies and gentlemen, this book is phenomenal.</span>
  <a data-text-id="1529683503405510784" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
